Mondelez CEO on growth, its snacking future and e-commerce|http://www.cnbc.com/netnet|http://www.cnbc.com/video/2018/09/07/mondelez-ceo-shifting-towards-other-channels-like-e-commerce-dirk-van-de-put-campbells-growth-oreos.html||2018-09-07|Source||Mondelez CEO on growth, its snacking future and e-commerce

10:15 AM ET Fri, 7 Sept 2018

Dirk Van de Put, Mondelez International CEO, sits down with CNBC's Sara Eisen at the Mondelez International Investors Day in Boston to discuss the company's growth, e-commerce, the future of brands and its shift from margins to top-line growth. He also mentioned that the earnings will grow three to five percent in 2019.
